{"tid":2232702,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"(iOS/AN)  精神病 情緒病 其實好得返","createTime":"2020-10-06T14:25:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T05:11:28.000Z","uid":375922,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e251ef2a404f14b861ace7c5aa874438e14824ac","tid":2232702,"uid":375922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T14:25:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EYsLWRw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEYsLWRw.jpg&h=30c4a4b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當我哋有負面情緒嘅時候我哋會同人講，但係身邊嘅人會話「你開心啲，諗開啲就得」。而有精神病嘅就更加嚴重，因為社會普遍對精神病唔了解，認為係患者有問題。我哋團隊都有成員經歷緊精神病，令我哋明白同路人嘅幫助同陪伴有幾咁重要。<br />\n<br />\n我哋用咗一個月開發「Mentalok慢得樂」手機應用程式。<br />\n<br />\n呢個平台嘅特點係，<br />\n1. 針對情緒困擾者而設計嘅對話平台<br />\n2. 我哋希望將病友嘅病歷變成「資歷」，透過分享生活經驗，增加大家嘅復元機會<br />\n<br />\n可能你會問：「將病友放埋一齊會唔會構成風險呢？」其實呢個模式一直係唔同既平台存在，我哋只係利用緊一個新嘅方法去延續呢個模式。如果有風險就放棄去做，咁仲會有咩人知道同滿足病友嘅需要？<br />\n<br />\n我哋邀請大家下載呢個app，因為呢個平台係適合所有人。就算你無情緒困擾，你都可以成為「社區支援人士」幫助病友。<br />\n<br />\n另外我哋都花左啲時間整咗條教學影片比大家，入面見！！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QKu5urxNlJ0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQKu5urxNlJ0&d=zpUJ%2F0Jv8gnTBnB6SvMaKFm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=004bca68\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QKu5urxNlJ0</a><br />\n<br />\n==========<br />\n<br />\n立即喺App Store及Google Play下載「Mentalok 慢得樂」手機應用程式啦！<br />\n<br />\nApp Store下載: <a href=\"https://apple.co/30lm9id\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapple.co%2F30lm9id&d=zpUJ%2F0Jv8gnTBnB6SvMaKFm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=7f67ab08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apple.co/30lm9id</a><br />\nGoogle Play下載: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/3n3PGqE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3n3PGqE&d=zpUJ%2F0Jv8gnTBnB6SvMaKFm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=289f8a9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3n3PGqE</a><br />\n<br />\n官方網站: <a href=\"https://mentalok.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmentalok.io&d=zpUJ%2F0Jv8g